{"tid":371471,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎講下自己有咩小動作","createTime":"2017-08-23T17:08:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T12:12:05.000Z","uid":132227,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c85f283e25c55b2159a0410ab29180632854edc4","tid":371471,"uid":132227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:08:49.000Z","msg":"今日唔覺意留意下人地小動作<br />\n有個啲手指好似彈琴咁整自己大脾<br />\n有個係到搓手<br />\n跟住留意下自己<br />\n乜小動作都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外仲有fd咬手指<br />\n<br />\n以前有人話過我緊張嗰陣會係咁撥頭髮<br />\n於是格硬克制住自己<br />\n有時又覺得人地啲小動作好礙眼<br />\n所以間唔中都留意下自己會唔會有小動作<br />\n於是而家咩小動作都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你地有咩小動作/身邊啲人有咩小動作<br />\n或者有冇咩特別嘢分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957009e2c55b47455aaaae08322421b9376226a4","tid":371471,"uid":32584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:13:46.000Z","msg":"同唔太熟既人出街/食飯會周圍望 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e0925bb92fd16439a096790c28b34f6ebbf6f4","tid":371471,"uid":11831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:14:29.000Z","msg":"唔舒服 暈 想嘔 會咬唇<br />\n緊張會咬手指"},{"pid":"2b5b188d1e940833a301693d2f2d707dd65081d8","tid":371471,"uid":59006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:16:34.000Z","msg":"捽碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e6ecda780339ad376001035e8afbd105cdb9862","tid":371471,"uid":107042,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:17:44.000Z","msg":"緊張就要r j"},{"pid":"9de4a72e7be3f69c4db989b65af9ea6ef60200fd","tid":371471,"uid":131538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:18:54.000Z","msg":"無聊嗰陣時不時會捽鼻"},{"pid":"11d8a2d6c62d2eab3c35ad5cad9c44e38ca26f05","tid":371471,"uid":4550,"